[div class=p 
	"The setup for the Item 1 zip is surprising to me. I thought he was trying to conserve Item 1 energy for a delay scroll, but no. However, pausing wastes i-frames, and the old setup barely seems to work as it is, so I'm guessing this is the best way to get hit 
	[em 
		"after
	]em
	" switching.
	$LF
