[div class=p 
	"This time, compared to the previous movie, the bug provided by 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/warmCabin 
		"warmCabin
	]a
	" was used. the pillar-type monsters that appear in the first two levels can be walked through without injury, which helps a lot in the first and second levels.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Another thing is that the Wily Castle stage 4 bosses were not carefully studied before when doing the 
	(__wikiLink|href=/5415M|implicitdisplaytext=5415M)
	", and after half a day of fighting one short of always hitting it. After all, it was a step short. This time in the normal mode was picked up is not a loss. bug advantage in the do not have to tear down the wall, this saves a lot of time, there is also a can avoid in the water of the crazy frame drop.
	$LF
